'''莎拉·克尔尼奇'''（{{lang-sr-Latn|Sara Krnjić}}，{{lang-sr-Cyrl|Сара Крњић}}，{{bd|1991年|7月15日||}}）生于诺维萨德，是一名塞尔维亚女子篮球运动员，场上位置是中锋<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/player/p/pid/57534/sid/6242/tid/96799/_/2014_FIBA_World_Championship_for_Women/index.html|title=Sara Krnjic's profile|work=FIBA|accessdate=2021-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212192019/http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/player/p/pid/57534/sid/6242/tid/96799/_/2014_FIBA_World_Championship_for_Women/index.html|archivedate=2019-12-12}}</ref>。她最初代表伏伊伏丁那女子篮球俱乐部参加塞尔维亚联赛。2008年，她加入MiZo Pécs 2010俱乐部，参加[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]联赛。2011年，她参加WNBA选秀，结果排名第35位，被[[華盛頓神秘|華盛頓神秘]]选中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/wnba/draft/2011.html|title=2011 WNBA Draft|work=Basketball Reference|accessdate=2021-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020152135/https://www.basketball-reference.com/wnba/draft/2011.html|archivedate=2020-10-20}}</ref>。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regeneracomsports.com/en/news/165/sara-krnjic-has-signed-with-regeneracom-sports/|title=SARA KRNJIC has signed with Regeneracom Sports|work=Regeneracom Sports|date=2019-08-24|accessdate=2021-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218170517/http://www.regeneracomsports.com/en/news/165/sara-krnjic-has-signed-with-regeneracom-sports/|archivedate=2020-02-18}}</ref>

